id: pm-lt6n
title: "GH-427: Windows Node 24 nightly fails — POSIX-only error-code assertions (EACCES/EISDIR) in restore-command and history-rewrite specs"
description: "Nightly Validation run 28698219516 (2026-07-04, windows-latest/Node 24): 4 test failures. restore-command.spec asserts rejects.toMatchObject({code:'EACCES'}) after chmod 0o444 on the history file, but Windows Node 24 raises EPERM when opening a read-only file for append. history-rewrite.spec asserts EISDIR when writing to a directory path; Windows raises EPERM. Fix: platform-tolerant assertions (EACCES|EPERM, EISDIR|EPERM)."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 2
tags[3]: ci,tests,windows
